'''鼬眼蛤科'''（学名：{{lang|la|Galeommatidae}}）屬於[[鼬眼蛤總科|鼬眼蛤總科]]。舊屬[[帘蛤目|帘蛤目]]，但按2019年的最新分類，本科成為了[[不等蛤總目|不等蛤總目]][[鼬眼蛤目|鼬眼蛤目]]的成員{{r|WoRMS_226}}<ref name="WoRMS_1326015">{{WoRMS |id=1326015 |title=Galeommatida |db=MolluscaBase |last=Bieler |first=Rüdiger |date=2019-02-10 |access-date=2019-10-10 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |url=https://royalsocietypublishing.org/doi/10.1098/rspb.2018.2684 |last1=Lemer |first1=S. |last2=Bieler |first2=R. |authorlink2=Rüdiger_Bieler |last3=Giribet |first3=G. |title=Resolving the relationships of clams and cockles: dense transcriptome sampling drastically improves the bivalve tree of life |journal=''[[Proceedings_of_the_Royal_Society_B:_Biological_Sciences|Proceedings of the Royal Society B: Biological Sciences]]'' |volume=286 |issue=1896 |page=20182684 |doi=10.1098/rspb.2018.2684 |language=en }}</ref>。

==分類==
根據[[WoRMS|WoRMS]]，本科現時包括49個屬{{r|WoRMS_226}}。以下為部分本科的屬{{r|Coan 2012}}：
* [[鼬眼蛤屬|鼬眼蛤屬]]（''Galeomma'' <small>Turton, 1825</small>）<ref name="WoRMS_138029">{{WoRMS |id=138029 |last1=Gofas |first1=S. |last2=Bouchet |first2=P. |year=2014 |title=''Galeomma'' Turton, 1825 |date=2014-12-31 }}</ref>
* [[小鼬眼蛤屬|小鼬眼蛤屬]]（''Galeommella'' <small> Habe, 1958</small>）<ref name="WoRMS_574687">{{WoRMS |id=138029 |last1=Tran |first1=Bastien |last2=Bouchet |first2=P. |year=2014 |title=''Galeommella''  Habe, 1958 |date=2012-01-01 }}</ref>
**[[秘魯小鼬眼蛤|秘魯小鼬眼蛤]] ''Galeommella peruviana'' (Olsson, 1961)
** ''[[Galeommella_utinomii|Galeommella utinomii]]'' Habe, 1958
* [[擬鼬眼蛤屬|擬鼬眼蛤屬]] （''Pseudogaleomma'' <small> Habe, 1964</small>）<ref name="WoRMS_592657">{{WoRMS |id=592657 |last=Bouchet |first=P. |authorlink=菲利普·布歇特 |title=''Pseudogaleomma''  Habe, 1958 |date=2012-01-01 }}</ref>
*[[红蛤属|红蛤属]]（''Scintilla'' <small>Deshayes, 1856</small>）

此外[[德文蛤属|德文蛤属]]（''Devonia'' <small>Turton, 1825</small>）{{r|WoRMS_138182}}、及[[沃尔多蛤属|沃尔多蛤属]]（''Waldo'' <small>[[William_Healey_Dall|Dall]], 1876</small>）{{r|WoRMS_196912|Val-S}}原為本科成員，今屬[[寄生蛤科|寄生蛤科]]。

